n" src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w256h256/2022/12/android-chrome-192x192.png" alt="FOSS Weekly #23.43：新的 Peppermint Mini 发行版、Remmina 指南和更多 Linux 内容"><span class="kg-bookmark-author">这是 FOSS</span> <span class="kg-bookmark-publisher">Abhishek Prakash</span></div></div> <div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/10/find-and-remove-deleted-files.png" alt="FOSS Weekly #23.43：新的 Peppermint Mini 发行版、Remmina 指南和更多 Linux 内容"></div></a></figure><p>这是<a href="https://itsfoss.com/install-chromium-ubuntu/">在 Ubuntu 上获取开源 Chromium 浏览器的</a>非 Snappy 方法。</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"> <a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://itsfoss.com/install-chromium-ubuntu/"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">在 Ubuntu Linux 中安装 Chromium 浏览器【Deb 和 Snap】</div><div class="kg-bookmark-description">学习在 Ubuntu 中安装 Chromium 浏览器，Snap 和 Deb 版本方法都已涵盖。</div> <div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w256h256/2022/12/android-chrome-192x192.png" alt="FOSS Weekly #23.43：新的 Peppermint Mini 发行版、Remmina 指南和更多 Linux 内容"><span class="kg-bookmark-author">这是 FOSS</span> <span class="kg-bookmark-publisher">Abhishek Prakash</span></div></div> <div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/10/install-chromium-ubuntu.png" alt="FOSS Weekly #23.43：新的 Peppermint Mini 发行版、Remmina 指南和更多 Linux 内容"></div></a></figure><hr><h2 id="%F0%9F%93%B9-what-we-are-watching"> 📹我们在看什么</h2><p>Linux Cast 的视频展示了<a href="https://yast.opensuse.org/?ref=itsfoss.com" rel="noreferrer">YaST</a>的强大功能！ </p><figure class="kg-card kg-embed-card"><iframe width="200" height="113" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bQ6Z1OTC_G0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen title="有史以来最强大的 Linux 工具！"></iframe></figure><hr><h2 id="%E2%9C%A8-p